The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detectives Matt and Frankie make their way to the town of Coffeyville where they run into the Dalton brothers who are seeking to commit a double bank robbery. Also starring Myron healey, Robert Bray and Robert Foulk. Look for future Daniel Boone/Davy Crocket star Fess Parker as a member of the Dalton gang. Episode originally aired in 1954.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detective Matt Clark and his partner Frankie head to Tombstone, Arizona to find Doc Holliday with suspicion that Holliday is involved in the gang activity there. Starring Jim Davis, Mary Castle, Kim Spalding, Frank Richards, James Craven amd Harry Harvey. Directed by William Witney. Episode originally aired in 1954. Series won an Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. In this episode, Deputy Jeff Taggart is cheated in a horse deal. When the trader is found murdered, Jeff is the chief suspect. Judge Bean has to discover the actual murderer to save his friend from the gallows. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this episode, Judge Bean appoints himself as the legal guardian of a young man whose father was a member of an outlaw gang. Beans reward -- the boys uncle puts a $3000 bounty on his head ! Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: The bank is robbed and the sheriff is killed while everyone is distracted by the wedding between Sand Creeks newspaper editor and a beautiful brunette. The sheriff being the editors best man, the grief-stricken editor begins to escalate the anger towards a suspected drifter with his bias reporting. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Annie is on the case when homesteaders are forced to sell their land for cheap due to suspicious circumstances. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: An editor of a newspaper is framed for murder. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in December, 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A doll seems to cast a spell on Little Snowbird (Rochelle Goldstein). Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in December, 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: After shooting Luke Grayson in self-defense, Ben Cartwright must protect himself from Graysons son, Todd, who seeks to avenge his fathers death.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC.

programme.title: Under Western Stars
programme.desc: Roy Rogers debuts in his starring role as the likable cowboy sent to Congress with a mission: let Washington know about the suffering of farmers in the wake of Americas 1930s Dustbowl. Enjoy the singing cowboy in his first starring role, rubbing shoulder with politians, going up against greedy executives, and representing a whole people group youll see why Rogers became a national icon! Frog Millhouse: Smiley Burnett. Elanore Fairbanks: Carol Hughes. John Fairbanks: Guy Usher. Plus music and singing from the Maple City Four. (The song Dust was nominated for an Academy Award!) Directed by Joe Kane.

programme.title: Man from Music Mountain
programme.desc: Gene Autry stops singing long enough to take on some nasty land developers in this oldtime western from Republic Pictures. Of course, it wouldnt be a Gene Autry movie if there werent at least a few songs, and this one comes packed with such numbers as Im Beginning to Care, Love, Burning Love, and the title song. Genes longtime sidekick Smiley Burnette gets to sing a few, too, including She Works Third Tub at the Laundry.

programme.title: Public Cowboy No. 1
programme.desc: Gene Autry and Smiley Burnette are back, and this time theyre dealing with some very modern thinking rustlers. These new criminals have taken up the latest technologies to outsmart the authorities, including shortwave radios and airplanes! Can Gene and Smiley get em? You bet! Songs include The West Aint What It Used To Be, I Got the HeebieJeebie Blues, and The Defective Detective from Brooklyn. Gene also gets romantic when he sings, I Picked up the Trail when I Found You...

programme.title: Daniel Boone
programme.desc: In 1775, Daniel Boone (George OBrien) leads thirty colonial families to Kentucky where they face the threats of Native American marauders led by rebel Simon Girty (John Carradine). Thats just the beginning, for there are even more dangers and clashes ahead for Boone and his party. With a cast that includes Ralph Forbes, Heather Angel, and lovable child star Dickie Jones, director David Howard takes us through one of the most exciting periods in American history!

programme.title: Rawhide
programme.desc: Baseball superstar Gehrig is one of several ranchers being coerced by a bunch of bandits. His sister and her lawyer/lover organize the ranchers. Directed by Ray Taylor; starring Smith Ballew, Gehrig, Evelyn Knapp. Talk about stunt casting! Gehrig was a New York Yankees star who was nearing the end of his career, but one of the biggest sports stars in the country. In the movie he plays a variation of himself, as Lou Gehrig, a retired baseball player who takes up ranching. Lou expects to relax on his ranch but quickly joins other ranchers in a fight to protect their properties.

programme.title: Winds of the Wasteland
programme.desc: John Wayne stars in this Republic Pictures western about the final days of the Pony Express. Former rider John Blair (Wayne) enters a coach race to win a $25,000 government mail contract, but there are dozens of obstacles in his path. The rest of the cast includes Lane Chandler and Phyllis Fraser, plus Lew Kelly (Lady of Burlesque) doing a great comic turn as Rocky OBrien, the eccentric, self-proclaimed mayor of a deserted mining town.

programme.title: Painted Desert
programme.desc: A mightly melodrama of red-blooded action, William Boyd stars in the Pre-Code western talkie - The Painted Desert (1931). The first sound film for Hollywood heavyweight Clark Gable, The Painted Desert finds Boyd and Gable at odds over the affections of a cowboys beautiful daughter (Helen Twelvetrees).

programme.title: Buffalo Stampede
programme.desc: A big time cast, including Randolph Scott, Buster Crabbe, Barton MacLane, and Harry Carey star in this feature about stampedes, Indian attacks, and plundering thieves! Directed by the esteemed Henry Hathaway (True Grit, Niagara).

programme.title: Adventures of Gallant Bess
programme.desc: Rather than a gorgeous Hollywood starlet, actor Cameron Mitchell (Carousel), playing cowboy Ted Daniels, shares the screen in this film with a magnificent wild horse named Gallant Bess, who he tames, trains and keeps for himself. But after Ted is gravely injured in a fixed rodeo, Bess is stolen away from him and forced to join a cruel traveling carnival in this fast-paced western from director Lew Landers (The Adventures of Rin Tin Tin).

programme.title: Gunsmoke Ranch
programme.desc: Flagg is relocating flood victims to Gunsmoke Ranch. The Three Mesquiteers know Flagg to be a crook and try to warn them. They ignore the warning and improve the land only to find that it has been condemned for a new dam.

programme.title: Law of the Pampas
programme.desc: Murder below the Equator...and Hopalong Cassidy races to action in the heart of the wild Pampas country !Hoppy (William Boyd) and his pal Lucky (Russell Hayden) head to South America to look after a herd of cattle sold by Cassidys boss to an Argentine rancher. Unfortunately, the scoundrel Ralph Merritt (Sidney Blackmer) wants the cattle, and hes not above hiring some dangerous characters to do his dirty work. Its a test of blazing guns...under a blazing sun! Can the boys of Bar 20 lay down the law in a lawless place like the Pampas? Can Hoppy and his gang succeed in what is truly a last frontier? Watch and see!

programme.title: A Lust to Kill
programme.desc: An imprisoned outlaw escapes and goes on the hunt for his brothers murderers, who just happen to be members of the outlaws own gang. He and his beloved hit the trail, but are pursued by local law enforcement, who have their own plans for justice. Starring Don Megowan, Jim Davis, and Allison Hayes.

programme.title: The Fighting Redhead
programme.desc: When a rustler named Faro kills one of his own henchmen and blames it on Sheila OConner, Red and Little Beaver set out to clear Sheila and to find evidence against Faro and his gang.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The Cartwrights try to invalidate a Spanish land grant to stop the De La Cuesta family from taking part of the Ponderosa and all of the Carson Valley settlers land.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.sub-title: S01 : E22 Blood on the Land
programme.desc: Adam Cartwright finds himself hostage to Jeb, a dangerous sheep herder who wants Ben to sign over a large plot of land.Starring Michael Landon as Little Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben helps three deserters, escaped from an Army stockade. Learning what they had to deal with, Ben promises to share the truth with his friend who is in charge of the fort.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Ben and Adam are in jail, about to be hung for a crime they didnt commit. Joe and Hoss must find out why the witnesses to the alleged crime have lied about what happened before the execution takes place. They receive help from a vagrant named Lassiter who is looking for the men who committed a lynching in Kansas years ago.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The son of a neighboring rancher intends to sell their land for a mining operation that will ruin the water rights agreement that Andy and Ben made years ago. Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: The Cartwrights take a young boy to the Ponderosa after the death of his mother. Hoss is the only one that is able to get through the boys hostility and bitterness, but, as the two begin to get close, the boys father breaks out of prison and comes to retrieve the boy.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.desc: Bobbie Jo falls head over heals for an edgy young poet from New York. He likes her, too, but hes not fond of Hooterville. Of coure, Kate has to show Bobby Jo what this pompous fool is all about. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963. Look for Dennis Hopper as the beatnik.

programme.desc: The family wants Billie Jo to become a doctor, but she wants to go to Hollywood to become an actress. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough. And be sure to look for Adam West in a pre-Batman role as Doctor Clayton Harris. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in January, 1964.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Billie Jo recieves an endowment, but instead of using it for medical school, she wishes to go to Hollywood.Kate meets with Judge Drucker to see if she can legally prevent the girl from goinng. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E19 Visit from a Big Star
programme.desc: A famous movie star (John Vivyan) stays at the Shady Rest Hotel. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Ralph Levy. Episode first aired January 28, 1964

Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Episode first aired in 1963.

Episode first aired in 1963.

programme.title: Custers Last Stand
programme.desc: The survivor of an Indian attack acquires a rare medicine arrow, and a menacing character named Blade (Reed Howes) will stop at nothing to take it from him. Elmer Clifton (Assassin of Youth, Seven Doors to Death) directs a memorable cast that includes Rex Lease (The Sign of the Wolf, The Monster Walks), Lona Andre (Slaves in Bondage, Death in the Air), and William Farnum (Samson and Delilah). Meanwhile, Frank McGlynn Jr is in the title role of General George A. Custer.

programme.title: Cowboy And The Prizefighter
programme.desc: Red Ryder takes Steve Stevenson, who has saved his life, to his ranch and gives him a job. Reds aunt, the Duchess, knew Steves father, who supposedly committed suicide after losing his ranch betting on a prizefight. Steve refuses to believe that his father took his own life, suspecting he was murdered. Red and Little Beaver aid Steve in finding his father killer.

programme.title: Riders of Destiny
programme.desc: John Wayne sings! Well, not really. His voice was dubbed here, but as Singin Sandy Saunders hes still able to write the code of justice with a blazing sixgun! Hes a government agent out to help a group of ranchers in their battle with a villain who is tying up local water rights. Also starring Gabby Hayes, Al St. John, Yakima Canutt, and Cecilia Parker, Riders of Destiny was filmed early in Waynes career it was his first for Lone Star but the unmistakable swagger is already in place!

programme.title: Santa Fe Trail
programme.desc: Oscar winner Michael Curtiz (Casablanca, Mildred Pierce) directed this exciting drama about Army officer Jeb Stuart and the days leading up to the Civil War. Errol Flynn (The Adventures of Robin Hood) stars as Stuart, with Olivia de Havilland as his romantic interest (the seventh of nine times they were paired together by Warner Bros.) The cast includes Ronald Reagan as General George Custer, and Raymond Massey as John Brown, with such familiar faces as Alan Hale and Van Hefflin in supporting roles. Filmed partly in Santa Fe!

programme.title: Ghost Town Gold [The Three Mesquiteers]
programme.desc: CAVALIERS OF THE CACTUS COUNTRY--ALWAYS READY FOR A FIGHT OR A FROLICK! The second entry in what would grow into a wildly popular series of Western Three Mesquiteers B-Movies produced by Republic Pictures, Ghost Town Gold tracks the titular trio as they attempt to recover the gold stolen by a gang in its effort to ruin the bank/mayor who ordered them to leave town. Frequent John Wayne collaborator Joseph Kane adds his signature directorial panache to this rousing shoot-em-up, setting the tone for a film series that was so rampantly successful, it spawned 50 sequels and a host of imitators from rival studios.

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Bleeder
programme.desc: Louise alskar Leo djupt, hjartligt och unreservedly och lyckligtvis glad nar hon upptacker hon ar gravid. Men for Leo ar den oforutsedda graviditetsfallet, Det får koppen att stromma over. Barnet betyder ett bestamt farval for hans sista, glittrande hopp att bryta ut ur den sorgliga miljon och bli något.

programme.title: Kommissarie Spack
programme.desc: Kommissarie Mårten Spack har kallats till en brottsplats dar en kropp hittats genomborrade med knivar, gafflar, skedar och en hogaffel. Till allas forvåning drar Kommissarie Spack slutsatsen att det ror sig om ett sjalvmord. Spack ser kopplingar till andra sjalvmord och konstaterar att kåren fått en galen seriesjalvmordare på halsen. Han kommer snart på andra tankar nar hans råbarkade kollega Grunvald Karlsson hittar andra spår  något som leder till något storre an vad de kunnat ana. En ny kollega, superpolisen Irene Snusk kopplas in på fallet. Tillsammans ska trion losa ett av de viktigaste fallen i svensk kriminalhistoria.

programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Del 2
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Pax
programme.desc: En flygmotor exploderar, och planet stortar mot marken. Mycket tyder på att detta ar slutet for alla ombord. Men for några av dem ar det en ny borjan. I luften mellan Stockholm och Oslo foljer vi sju personer och ett hjarta på vag från en kropp till en annan. Nar den tunga maskinen faller ser de livet i ett annat ljus. Aldrig ar livet så narvarande som nar slutet narmar sig. I detta storslagna, romantiska och nargångna dramas ensemble finns flera av Sveriges mest namnkunniga skådespelare, bland annat Samuel Froler, Thomas von Bromssen, Bjorn Granath, Annika Hallin och Marika Lagercrantz.

programme.title: Mannen utan minne
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om en man som tappar sitt minne och får hjalp av fattiga men storhjartade manniskor i en containerby.

programme.title: Den Svavelgula Himlen
programme.desc: Forfattaren Frej blev i tonåren kar i overklasstjejen Stella Rabell. Deras starka band overlevde mot alla odds det stormiga forhållandet under decennierna som foljde. Nar Stellas storebror Alex blir knivhuggen borjar Frej tanka tillbaka till saker som har hant från det lyckliga 70-talet och framåt.

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Brott och straff
programme.desc: En filmatisering av Dostojevskijs roman med samma namn, som utspelar sig i 1980-talets Finland. Romanen Brott och straff ar ansedd som en av vår tids storsta litterara verk. Fjodor Dostojevskij målar upp det moraliska dilemmat huruvida ett brott, i det har fallet ett mord ar forsvarbart om resultatet blir positivt for många, om andamålet helgar medlen. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: Moln på drift
programme.desc: Ilona och Lauri ar ett stravsamt par som inte begar mycket av livet. Tak over huvudet, mat på bordet, ett glas vin och en kvall framfor tv-n. De arbetar plikttroget och agnar sina korta ledigheter åt varandra och sin hund. Men en dag hander något som hotar att slå deras trygga tillvaro i spillror. En varm och absurd historia om ett alldeles vanligt par någonstans i Finland.

programme.title: Skuggor i paradiset
programme.desc: Nikander ar en ensam sopbils-chauffor som en dag moter den anspråkslosa snabbkopskassorskan Ilona. Nikander blir blixtrande kar, men deras omsesidiga blyghet medfor att det romantiska lyser med sin frånvaro. Så plotsligt andras livet… Ilona får sparken och de bestammer sig for att traffas på ett mysigt litet motell. Aki Kaurismaki ar kand for sina socialrealistiska skildringar och svarta karleksforklaringar till ett dystert Finland. Filmer med komiska och omsinta inslag.

programme.title: 6 Juni
programme.desc: Samira ar en 24-årig, glad och sot tjej som borde ha sin basta tid i livet framfor sig. Men hennes familj har beslutat att hon ska giftas bort till en man hon inte alskar. Om hon inte gor det riskerar hon att utsattas for hedersmord. Hasse ar en medelålders man som sitter på kåken for att avtjana ett straff for rattfylla. Han ska mucka om en vecka och langtar efter att få leva ett nyktert liv tillsammans med sin hustru och son.Gertrud ar en anka sedan nio år som inte kan slappa taget kring sin bortgångne make Gustav. Men grannen Bertil tycker att det ar på tiden att hon bestammer sig for om hon vill borja om på nytt med honom.

programme.title: Lindell - Sorgmanteln - Del 1
programme.desc: Fyra små flickor på ett fotografi. Tjugo år senare hittas en av dem mordad. En annan ar spårlost forsvunnen. Cato Isaksen ar redo att losa nya kriminalgåtor. Lise Sommer blir upphunnen av sitt forflutna. Hennes basta van Esther Synnøve Lønn har hittats mordad med avskuren hals. Några dagar senare forsvinner Esthers son. Nar polisen borjar att skrapa på ytan visar det sig att en barndomsvan till Lise och Esther Synnøve också saknas. Forhållandet mellan vaninnorna doljer morka understrommar. Vad var det egentligen som hande nar flickorna var små? Och deras mammor - vad doljer de?

programme.title: Lindell: Dromfångaren - Del 2
programme.desc: En olidligt spannande kriminalhistoria dar de psykologiska undertonerna bar handlingen framåt tills det hela slutar i en dramatisk kapplopning med en iskall mordare. Vem ar fonstertittaren som som står och betraktar de unga kvinnorna i lagenheten mitt emot? Har han något med mordet på nittonåriga Therese Geber att gora? Är det samma man som tar sig in i deras lagenhet på natterna? Kriminalkommissarie Cato Isaksen får ett nytt fall på halsen.

programme.title: Projekt Z
programme.desc: En grupp filmstudenter tar med sig tre lediga skådespelare till ett nedlagt hotell i de norska fjallen for att spela in en zombiefilm. Deras fiktion blir plotsligt verklighet nar en okand varelse borjar terrorisera filminspelningen.

programme.title: Klanen - berattelsen om Grudornas slakt
programme.desc: "Klanen" ar historien om en brottslig slakt dar Mika Kaurismaki behandlar existensens villkor genom den traditionella episka formen, på gransen mellan ratt och fel i lagen. Alexander, den yngsta sonen, ar slaktens vita får. Han forvantas hålla sig på den raka vagen, till skillnad från sin far och andra man i slakten. Men familjen ar varst, och blod ar tjockare an vatten... Familjedramat "Klanen" ar en storslagen hyllning till den gamla finska filmen.

programme.title: Kommissarie Spack
programme.desc: Kommissarie Mårten Spack har kallats till en brottsplats dar en kropp hittats genomborrade med knivar, gafflar, skedar och en hogaffel. Till allas forvåning drar Kommissarie Spack slutsatsen att det ror sig om ett sjalvmord. Spack ser kopplingar till andra sjalvmord och konstaterar att kåren fått en galen seriesjalvmordare på halsen. programme.title: Cha Cha Cha
programme.desc: Den alkoholiserade Matti (Matti Pellonpaa), som bor under broarna, ar på vag att arva en betydande summa pengar från sin amerikanska faster. Men mannen måste vara representativ under fasterns besok. Matti berattar om situationen for sin van som arbetar som bilhandlare, och denne foreslår en rollbyten mot ersattning.

programme.title: Zombie och spoktåget
programme.desc: Zombie (Silu Seppala: Leningrad Cowboys) ar en individ som går sin egen vag och inte kan folja de normer som det finska samhallet har satt for honom. Zombie beslutar sig for att lamna allt och ge sig utomlands - till en plats dar ingen forvantar sig något av honom. Zombie och spoktåget betraktas av många som några av Mika Kaurismakis basta filmer. Filmen belonades med Jussi-priset for Basta regissor, Basta manliga huvudroll och Basta foto år 1992. Tragikomiskt och aven surrealistiskt foljer Zombie med bland andra Mato Valtonen och Sakke Jarvenpaa från Sleepy Sleepers, samt naturligtvis Matti Pellonpaa.

programme.title: Så olika
programme.desc: Så olika ar en komedi om karlek. Det kretsar kring två systrar, den ena nytillsatt finansborgarråd i Stockholm, nyskild och mamma till två dottrar. Den andra en sjalvstandig TV-producent som har fått i uppdrag att gora ett nytt direktsant sångprogram från Skansen - nu mitt bland djuren! Den handlar om att bli sanslost foralskad i sin varsta fiende, om manniskor som mots trots att de ar fundamentalt olika. For har overvinner karleken allt - från politisk maktkamp till dans med salarna på Skansen.

programme.title: Ettor and Nollor - Del 2
programme.desc: FBI och Interpol får nys om en stor kreditkortsharva och pundaren Sebbe plockas in som misstankt. Nar polisen borjar sina forhor får de hora en otrolig historia från Goteborgs undre varld. Svenska och ryska gangsters, marockanska hackers, korrupta politiker och giriga kostymnissar - alla vill tjana stora pengen, ingen vill vara hunden...

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Long Story Short
programme.desc: Det har ar berattelsen om Ellen och hennes vanner, och deras mer eller mindre sjalvforvållat komplicerade karleksliv och romantiska drommar. Tre år av vannernas basta och samsta karlekshistorier sammanfattas och berattas genom åtta kapitel, som alla utspelar sig vid olika festliga tillstallningar. Gruppen kampar med iden om det perfekta forhållandet och måste omvardera vad sann karlek egentligen ar.

programme.title: A Polar Year
programme.desc: 28-årige Anders bestammer sig for att resa till Gronland for att undervisa i en liten by. Hans foraldrar tar avstånd från beslutet eftersom de forvantar sig att han ska ta over familjegården, men Anders ser garna ett miljoombyte och nya utmaningar. Livet ar tufft i den lilla byn – tuffare an Anders hade forestallt sig. Byborna tar till en borjan inte emot honom val och om han ska gora sig några forhoppningar om att hjalpa familjerna – inte minst barnen – måste Anders ta ett viktigt beslut. Han måste lara kanna byns manniskor och inte minst deras traditioner. Forst nar han gjort det kommer en helt ny varld att oppna sig for Anders...

programme.title: Bitchkram
programme.desc: Kristin raknar dagarna till studenten då hon antligen får lamna småstaden och sin manipulativa syster for sina drommars New York. Allt ar perfekt och lokaltidningen på orten har lovat att publicera Kristins kronikor om staden som aldrig sover. Men Kristin missar planet och gommer sig istallet hemma hos Andrea, en marklig ung tjej, långt ute på landet for att undvika total fornedring. I huset ingenstans tar Kristin med Andrea till New Yorks pulserande hjarta i ett vindlande virtuellt aventyr som alla darhemma kan folja i hennes artiklar. Men så tranger sig verkligheten på.

programme.title: Calamari Union
programme.desc: Sjutton unga man, varav sexton heter Frank och bar svarta glasogon, lamnar en elandig arbetarmiljo och beger sig ut på en farlig resa genom storstaden på jakt efter den mytiska stadsdelen Eira. På grund av olika omstandigheter kommer bara två av dem fram. Men Eira ar inte riktigt det de hoppats på och deras sokande fortsatter – nu i en roddbåt mot Estland… Denna surrealistiska komedi ar Kaurismakis andra långfilm. En skon och absurd berattelse som blandar amerikansk gangsterfilm med finsk punk.

programme.title: Flickan från tandsticksfabriken
programme.desc: Iris ar trott på sitt dodstråkiga jobb och liv. For att pigga upp stamningen beger hon sig ut på stan och shoppar en rod klanning. Natten spenderar hon med en rik man som lamnar henne en summa pengar morgonen efter. En tid senare upptacker Iris att hon ar gravid och upplyser den formogne mannen om sin situation, han skickar en ny bunt sedlar och ber henne att gora abort. Då går Iris ut och koper en stor mangd råttgift.

programme.title: Lindell - Ormbararen - Del 1
programme.desc: Ett från forsta stund fangslande och skakande psykologiskt drama i vilket vansinnets logik driver handlingen mot ett oundvikligt klimax. Det går en seriemordare los i Oslo. For 43-årige nyskilde och nyforalskade Cato Isaksen och hans medarbetare på mordavdelningen vid Oslo-kriminalen blir det en kapplopning med tiden. For mordaren kommer att doda igen. På otackt vis vavs Cato Isaksens privatliv in i irrgångarna i den okande mordarens psyke. Nar det till slut går upp for Cato vem mordaren ar så ar det nastan for sent.

programme.title: De dodas tjarn
programme.desc: Inspirerad av boken ”De dodas tjarn” av Bernhard Borge. Lillians tvillingbror Bjorn dor på ett mystiskt satt ensam vid den gamla familjestugan. Nu, ett år senare, kommer Lillian med sina vanner till stugan for att ta farval och salja stallet. Strax efter ankomsten borjar underliga saker att handa. Lillian går i somnen och kan inte skilja mardrom från verklighet. Någon eller några jagar dem och till slut dyker ett lik upp. Är legenden om Tore Gruvik på vag att bli verklighet eller ar fienden en av dem? Vad skedde forra sommaren och vad var fel på Bjorn Werner?

programme.title: Lindell - Ormbararen - Del 2
programme.desc: Ett från forsta stund fangslande och skakande psykologiskt drama i vilket vansinnets logik driver handlingen mot ett oundvikligt klimax. Det går en seriemordare los i Oslo. For 43-årige nyskilde och nyforalskade Cato Isaksen och hans medarbetare på mordavdelningen vid Oslo-kriminalen blir det en kapplopning med tiden. For mordaren kommer att doda igen. programme.title: Simon Bates 70s Pop! Top 50
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Simon Bates 70s Pop! Top 50
programme.desc: Simon Bates with a celebration of a decade - the 50 biggest pure pop hits of the 70s. Hes got a bucketload of Boney M, oodles of the Osmonds and an armful of Abba!

programme.title: Bruno Brookes UK Top 40 of the 70s
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Bruno Brookes UK Top 40 of the 70s
programme.desc: Including 10 big million sellers back when it was a rare achievement! These are 40 of the biggest selling songs of the decade with Bay City Rollers, Abba, Queen, Blondie and Wings

programme.title: Retro Rewind! 70s Edition
programme.desc: From hippies to punk rockers, via folk, funk, soul and disco - these are the classic songs that made the 70s!

programme.title: Gone...But Not Forgotten Top 25
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Gone...But Not Forgotten Top 25
programme.desc: These 25 stars of rock and pop during the 70s are no longer with us. But the music from names like McVie, Bowie, Bolan, Marley, Mercury, Lennon and Presley will live on forever.

programme.title: The NOW Yearbook 1976
programme.desc: The hottest songs from the year of a record breaking summer! Simon Bates has the soundtrack of a great 12 months in pop, including Wings, Wild Cherry and The Wurzels!

programme.title: Simon Bates Rock Ballads! 1970-79
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Simon Bates Rock Ballads! 1970-79
programme.desc: We didnt yet call them Power Ballads, but some masters of the genre - Boston, Toto and Whitesnake - were already at it! Simes has 25 power pop love songs and ballads - in order.

programme.title: Wings v Fleetwood Mac!
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wings v Fleetwood Mac!
programme.desc: 70s soft rock heaven as we pit Macca against Mick in a totally contrived 70s band battle!

programme.title: Rocket Man! Elton in the 70s
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Rocket Man! Elton in the 70s

Trots att han också ar orsaken till många av dem.

programme.title: Modern Persuasion
programme.desc: En modern version av Jane Austens roman ”Övertalning”. Wren Cosgrove ar en lycklig och framgångsrik karriarkvinna som varje kvall kommer hem till sin katt. Nar hennes firma anlitas av Owen Jasper, han som var den ratte, så vacks gamla kanslor till liv och Wren får en ny chans att uppleva den sanna karleken.

programme.title: The Last Kiss
programme.desc: Michael och Jenna ar ett par, och liksom alla andra 30-something-par står de infor en rad val i sitt forhållande. Men samtidigt som forpliktelserna blir allt fler, traffar Michael den unga skonheten Kim .

programme.title: Broken English
programme.desc: Nora Wilder håller på att tappa hoppet. Alla i hennes narhet ar i ett forhållande, ar gifta eller har barn. Nora ar i 30-årsåldern, ensam med ett jobb hon inte trivs med och en mor som standigt tjatar om allt. Och så har vi ju hennes basta kompis Audreys "perfekta brollop". Efter flera misslyckade dater moter hon helt ovantat fransmannen Julien som har en stark passion for livet.

programme.title: Shes The Man
programme.desc: Nar Violas bror drar till London passar hon på att hanga på hans internatskola. Utkladd till sin bror blir Viola kar i en av fotbollsspelarna i skollaget men inser snart att det ar betydligt fl er an hon (han) som har karleksproblem… Duke vill ha Olivia som gillar Sebastian som egentligen ar Viola. Violas brorsa traffar Monique så hon hatar Olivia som hanger med Duke for att gora Sebastian svartsjuk. Sebastian ar ju egentligen Viola som ar kar i Duke som tror att hon ar en snubbe... Hangde ni med?

programme.title: Monte Carlo
programme.desc: Grace (Selena Gomez) ar en vanlig tjej som blir en oavsiktlig prinsessa nar en familjens sommarresa till Paris blir en livs fantasi. Lev som royalty, Grace, tillsammans med hennes två basta vanner, upptacker vem hon verkligen ar - genom att anta en andras identitet.

programme.title: Bad Cupid
programme.desc: Archie ar en gud på uppdrag att sakerstalla så karleken alltid vinner oavsett vad. Eller åtminstone någorlunda så nar som på att man kanske dor på kuppen for den som forsoker. Egentligen så ar han inte så noga med vad resultatet blir. Hans installning som Amors forlangda arm till romantik och karlek ar snarare ratt så halvhjartad, som man bor se upp for om man hamnar i hans vag nar ska forsoker komma med en hjalpande hand. Speciellt dom som han verkligen forsoker hjalpa.

programme.title: Dubbelt begar
programme.desc: Dubbelt begar berattar historien om den unga kvinnan Chloe, som benagen till depression påborjar terapi och dar blir foralskad i sin psykoterapeut Paul. Efter ett par månader flyttar hon in hos sin nya alskare men upptacker snabbt att han doljer en del av sin identitet for henne.

programme.title: Very Good Girls
programme.desc: New York-tjejerna Lily och Gerry ar basta vanner på det dar viset man bara ar som ung nar man har hela livet framfor sig. De gor upp en pakt om att forlora oskulden under den sista sommaren fore collegestudierna, men denna varma sommar satts deras vanskap for forsta gången på prov nar de råkar falla for en och samma kille. En oskuldsfull tid får sitt slut på fler an ett satt.

programme.title: Can You Keep a Secret
programme.desc: Emma sitter på ett plan som hon tror ar på vag att storta. Hon berattar darfor alla sina hemligheter for en snygg framling. Åtminstone tror hon att han ar en framling...tills hon traffar Jack, hennes foretags nya vd, som alltså vet varenda pinsam hemlighet om henne. Baserad på romanen med samma namn på New York Times bastsaljarlista, från forfattaren till ”En shopaholics bekannelser”, Sophie Kinsella.

programme.title: No Stranger Than Love
programme.desc: Vad kan vara konstigare an att ett stort hål oppnar sig i Lucy Sherringtons vardagsrumsgolv? Jo, karleken, som det visar sig.Det finns inte en man i stan som inte ar kar i Lucy. Hon ar snall, sympatisk, rolig och lojal – hon ar den perfekta tjejen som inte kan gora något fel. Ändå har hon gått med på en traff med Clint som ar gift och coach for footballaget. Precis nar de ska påborja sin affar trillar Clint ner i ett hål som oppnar sig i Lucys vardagsrum. Men det ar inte vilket hål som helst; det ar det eviga morkrets interdimensionella och enkelriktade hål. Clint fastnar nere i hålet och svavar runt i ett oandlighetens mellantillstånd.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Youth In Revolt
programme.desc: Michael Cera spelar rollen som Nick Twisp. En unik och alskvard tonåring med smak for livets sofistikerade gladjeamnen, såsom Sinatra och Fellini. På en campingsemester med familjen foralskar han sig i den vackra, intelligenta och frigjorda Sheeni Saunders (Portia Doubleday). Men geografi, familj och svartsjuka ex-partners konspirerar for att hålla Nick och Sheeni åtskilda. Efter uppmuntran från Sheeni overger Nick sitt tråkiga, forutsagbara liv och utvecklar ett rebelliskt alter ego: Francois Dillinger. Med mustasch, slips, djup rost och bad boy-attityd kan inget stoppa Francois från att vara tillsammans med Sheeni.

programme.title: The Last Kiss
programme.desc: Michael och Jenna ar ett par, och liksom alla andra 30-something-par står de infor en rad val i sitt forhållande. Men samtidigt som forpliktelserna blir allt fler, traffar Michael den unga skonheten Kim .

programme.title: Whats Your Number?
programme.desc: Ally Darling inleder en stravan efter att finna den basta "ex" av hennes liv, på något satt som behovs, nar hon laser en tidningsartikel som varnar for att manniskor som har haft 20 eller fler relationer har saknat sin chans till sann karlek. Allys hunky nya granne Colin (Chris Evans) hjalper henne att spåra hennes exes, i utbyte mot Ally som hjalper Colin att undvika hans.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: My Best Friends Girl
programme.desc: Tank (Dane Cook) moter det ultimata vanskapsprovet nar hans basta van (Jason Biggs) ber honom att ta ut hans ex (Kate Hudson) på en usel dejt for att hon ska forstå vilken bra pojkvan han ar.

programme.title: Shes The Man
programme.desc: Nar Violas bror drar till London passar hon på att hanga på hans internatskola. Utkladd till sin bror blir Viola kar i en av fotbollsspelarna i skollaget men inser snart att det ar betydligt fl er an hon (han) som har karleksproblem… Duke vill ha Olivia som gillar Sebastian som egentligen ar Viola. Violas brorsa traffar Monique så hon hatar Olivia som hanger med Duke for att gora Sebastian svartsjuk. Sebastian ar ju egentligen Viola som ar kar i Duke som tror att hon ar en snubbe... Hangde ni med?

programme.title: Warm Bodies
programme.desc: Karleken overvinner allt... till och med den oemotståndliga lusten att ata din alskades hjarnmassa! I en inte så avlagsen framtid ar jorden befolkad av lika delarmanniskoatande zombier och zombiebekampande manniskor. Men nar den unge zombien R plotsligt får impulsen att radda den varmblodiga flickan Julie från ett zombieoverfall borjar en vanskap som kommer att vanda upp och ner på nyavarldsordningen! Forutsatt att Julie kan hållasig levande – och R kan hålla sig levande dodtillrackligt lange!

programme.title: Broken English
programme.desc: Nora Wilder håller på att tappa hoppet. Alla i hennes narhet ar i ett forhållande, ar gifta eller har barn. Nora ar i 30-årsåldern, ensam med ett jobb hon inte trivs med och en mor som standigt tjatar om allt. Och så har vi ju hennes basta kompis Audreys "perfekta brollop". Efter flera misslyckade dater moter hon helt ovantat fransmannen Julien som har en stark passion for livet.

programme.title: Min sommarprins
programme.desc: PR-krischefen Deidre och hennes assistent Mandy flyger in nar den upproriske prinsen Colin grips i småstaden Idaho. Men nar Deidre moter ett eget fiasko, får Mandy ovantade karriar- (och romantiska) mojligheter.

programme.title: They Came Together
programme.desc: Nar Joel (Paul Rudd) och Molly (Amy Poehler) mottes var det hat vid forsta ogonkastet: hans storbolag Godiskompaniet hotade att stanga ner hennes bohemiska godisaffar. Plus att Joel fortfarande hade kanslor for sitt sexiga ex (Cobie Smulders). Men, trots allt så blir de kara, tills dess att de gor slut och Molly borjar dejta sin revisor (Ed Helms). Men, precis i sluttampen...tja, du får se helt enkelt. (Ledtråd: Joel håller ett stort tal och de hittar tillbaka till varandra.) Från regissoren som skapade Wet Hot American Summer, Wanderlust och Role Models kommer nu en helknapp och satirisk underminering av den romantiska komedigenren.

programme.title: Don Jon
programme.desc: Don Martell ar en kille från New Jersey, vars liv kretsar kring familjen, vannerna, kyrkan – och porr. Formågan att ragga upp nya tjejer varje helg har gett honom smeknamnet ”Don Jon”. En kvall traffar han den snygga och romantiska Barbara som letar efter en underbar dromkille, en idealbild som ar valdigt långt från Don.

programme.title: Love Hurts
programme.desc: Pauls kvinnoaffarer ersatts med flera komiska incidenter nar han måste tillbringa en helg med sina foraldrar, sin fore detta fru och barnen.

programme.title: Just Friends
programme.desc: Får vi presentera Chris Bander. Highschool på nittiotalet var en pina: han var blyg, overviktig och hemligt foralskad i Jamie, hans enda kompis och tillika en av skolans mest populara hejarklacksledare. Men nar han antligen hade lyckats samla mod nog att gora en framstot, ville hon bara att de skulle vara vanner! I dag ar Chris en aslacker skivproducent i LA och kan valja bland en uppsjo av vackra och villiga tjejer. Och nar han plotsligt blir strandsatt i sin gamla hemstad ser han chansen att forfora Jamie en gång och for alla. Men det ar nu inte så latt att ta steget från att vara "bara vanner" till att bli "knullkompisar".

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E04 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E06 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 6, Russia
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! Not only a tank pull was done here but also the Viking Press/ Deadlift Max and Log lift reps were spectacular events to see here in Russia. With Mikhail Koklyaev also as event presenter, the former top 3 world strongest man from Russia was there

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E07 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: In this year’s edition on The Balkan Peninsula, we have competing the new talent from Estonia Marko Remlik together with Sebastian Kurek from Poland and yellow leader Kelvin de Ruiter

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E08 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Mateusz Kieliszkowski from Poland and Aivars Smaukstelis from Latvia are the strongman future of these days. Mateusz is the best man in the World at the moment to defeat. Only 25 years and such a fantastic strongman. They come here only for a win. But there are 12 more Strong athletes in this episode who want the title of Finland as well.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E09 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Mateusz Is leading after day 1 (previous episode) with close behind him Aivars Smaukstelis and Zake Muluzi from the UK. All very exciting! 5 events in this episode: Log Lift, Fram Walk, Deadlift, Sack Throw (Weight for Height), Loading medley.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E10 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 10, Portugal
programme.desc: In this stage we have a new strong debutant: Oleg Sylka from the Ukraine. He is the new talent, who will stand up against the old champions like ZSydrunas Savickas and Brian Shaw and the Stoltman Brother from the UK. This new talent Oleg is a great character and we will see him flame in the episode in Portugal.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E11 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 11, Callio
programme.desc: In Callio is the deepest mine of Europe/ 1500 meter deep, whereas the MLO Strongman Champions League also did 1 event. The Forward Hold, on a 1500 dept/ also a kind of new record/ as it was never done before. Spectacular and new in Strongman sport.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E12 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 12, Ukraine
programme.desc: Kelvin de Ruiter is here to defend his SCL World Truck Pull Championships title. But this year, another strong field wants his title. Over 3 different pulls with 3 different trucks, and 14 athletes at the start, it will be difficult for everybody.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E13 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 13, Caribbean
programme.desc: SCL edition Curacao 2019 was a great event, twelve power boys from all over made a great show at the white beaches, and 35 degrees Celsius heat in the Carrabean Islands. Two events were held on Friday at the beach of beautiful resort Sunscape, the other three were held near the world famous floating bridge at Willemstad on Saturday night.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E14 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 14, Dubai
programme.desc: Hosted at Meydan Grandstand in Dubai, the Strongman Champions League had some really big names in the list like Mateusz Kieliszkowski from Poland, Brian Shaw from the USA and Krzysztof Radzikowski. In front of the Burj Khalifa the athletes do the deadlift max and 4 other heavy events at another spot in Dubai.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E15 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 15, World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: With new places on the calendar, over 16 stages, broadcasting in over 100 countries and in its 13th year, the MLO Strongman Champions League (SCL) can be seen truly as the biggest strongman league in the world. The last stage over 2 episodes of the MLO Strongman Champions League, were held in Porto, Portugal. This competition in Portugal is full of memorable performances and strong results.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E16 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 16, World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: With new places on the calendar, over 16 stages, broadcasting in over 100 countries and in its 13th year, the MLO Strongman Champions League (SCL) can be seen truly as the biggest strongman league in the world. This competition in Portugal is full of memorable performances and strong results and this is the final!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E01 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: The spectacular Fefor Arena hosted for the 8th time the Worlds Strongest Viking, part of the SCL World Series. But with the absence of former title holders its anyones game. Again, a very spectacular episode of the Strongman Champions League here in Norway.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E02 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 2, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: In this episode, the Titan, former double World champion from Latvia will compete against his fellow countryman and the current World champion - Aivars Smaukstelis. With 8 events over 2 stages the contestants are pushed to their limits in Finland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E03 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 3, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Dainis Zageris and Aivars Smaukstelis, both from Latvia have a serious, strong battle in the this second and final episode of the SCL Finland 2020. Watch the unbelievable and brute power of these athletes in the last 4 events to crown the winner.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E04 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 4, World Record Breakers
programme.desc: The SCL Germany event takes place in an ancient castle called Die Burg in the heart of Germany. Its here where 5 world record attempts take place across 5 different events with 10 athletes. They will go to the max! See this and much more in the SCL Germany 2020.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E05 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 5, Strongest Viking
programme.desc: SCL Norway is normally all about snow, wind, and cold weather. Our brave athletes are used to compete under conditions few other athletes have competed in, but after COVID delays the competition has been moved from winter to summer bringing in a whole new range of challenges. With an impressive athlete list who will be the winner across 5 cruel events?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E06 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 6, World Strongest Team 1
programme.desc: Were in sunny Finland for the next stage of a double-bill of SCL action, but this time its a team event. A truly fantastic event with 6000 spectators. Even during COVID times this was exceptional! 8 Strong Teams where fighting for the title over a crazy 9 events.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E07 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 7, World Strongest Team 2
programme.desc: Day 2 of the famous Team World championship here in Finland, done over 9 cruel events. In this episode the last and final 5 events take place. 8 Strong Teams are fighting for the title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E08 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 8, Portugal
programme.desc: The next set of challenges are set in sunny Esposende in Portugal. With stars such as Travis Ortmayer, Kelvin de Ruiter from Holland, and Ervin Toots from Estonia. While Fabio Silva will defend the honour in his own country.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E09 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 9, World Records (Part 1)
programme.desc: We are back in Germany, with the world record breakers. We promise you this is going to be amazing. Do not move from that seat, because we are going to see some records smashed today. Over 6 cruel events, you will see who gets crowned of the King Of The Castle!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E10 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 10, World Records (Part 2)
programme.desc: With the next episode of Strongman Champions League Germany. Its the world record breakers, and in the last show we set two new records. Can more be records be broken before the king of the castle is crowned?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E11 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 11, Worlds 105 Kg (Part 1)
programme.desc: Welcome to Kokkola in Finland. This city will be the setting for the Lightweight World championship. Out of 24 athletes, only 16 will make it through to the final day, but who will champion each event and who is going to be eliminated?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E12 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 12, Worlds 105 Kg (Part 2)
programme.desc: Its the second day, and the top 16 athletes have made it through to the final round. With another 4 events to go who will get the crown of world champion?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E13 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 13, Ukraine
programme.desc: Welcome to Ukraine and the wonderful capital city of Kyiv. Were here for the second time for the iconic truck pull World Championships! The reigning World champion Kelvin de Ruiter from Holland will defend his title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E14 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 14, Romania
programme.desc: In this episode, a final chance for our athletes to get vital world series ranking points on board to give them the best possible chance of success and an initial advantage at the finals. Its the last show before the world finals and the top 10 places are up for grabs, but who will they be?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E15 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 15, World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: We are in Alanya, on Turkeys south-coast for the final stop at the end of a mammoth season. Here in the sunshine, well finally crown our world champion and what a place Alanya is - you could not ask for a better setting. Aivars Smaukstellis, the reigning world champion is defending his title, and two-time world champion Dainis Zageris is also here, but with a though competition, who will win?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E16 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 16, World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: What a day ahead of us here in Alanya, just a handful of events to go before we find out who will be the winner of Strongman Champions League in 2021. These are the world finals, and all the big names are in the house. With just 3 events to go - who will take the crown of World Champion 2021 and be the STRONGEST?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E01 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 1, Finland Stage 1
programme.desc: We are back, after a short break it feels like we never even left. We’re here in Vaasa - Finland kicking off 2022 new world series. If you are watching at home, just like these people, you’re in the right place. Because this is a special edition world record breaker. The only question left today, is to see how many new world records will be set so stay tuned.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E02 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 2, Holland Part 1
programme.desc: We are here in Doetinchem – Holland, for Stage 2 and 3 in the hottest day of the year. 40-degree heat, these boys have to work harder than they ever have. The sun is going to be beating down, they’re going to be sweating, hydration is going to be key today. I also reckon they’re all going to be wearing their sunglasses. Let’s see which shady looking character wins.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E03 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 3, Holland Part 2
programme.desc: So there you have it. The next day, 3 more events in 40 Degrees heat. We’ve got Gavin coming into day 2 leading the pack. Kelvin De Ruiter our world champion struggling a little bit at the moment, but Yoke Race, Conan’s Wheel and then Stones to finish. There is a lot to be played for here, so stay tuned to see if Gavin can take the lead and beat Kelvin overall.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E04 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 4, Serbia Part 1
programme.desc: We’re in the Serbian city of Novi kozarci, for the next stage in the world series. And what a fantastic line up we have for you again. But it is going to be one of the hottest stages yet. A Strongman competition in 44-degree heat. It will be a real challenge for these athletes to finish this event. From all over the world the strongmen came here for the title! Welcome to the heat hell in Serbia.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E05 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 5, Serbia Part 2
programme.desc: Welcome to day 2 in Serbia, and its another baking hot one. We are in Kikinda today! We’ve got three more gruelling events for our athletes. Sami Ahola is leading the pack, so can he be the first Finnish athlete to take an SCL title. Stay tuned to find out.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E06 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 6, Joensuu Part 1
programme.desc: In this competition, we have our athletes paired up. They’re going to have to take on each event together, having to factor in each other’s strengths and possibly weaknesses. Can the men who normally work alone, share their powers as a duo? Let’s find out!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E07 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 7, Joensuu Part 2
programme.desc: Day 2 of the famous Team World championship here in Finland- Joensuu. Welcome to the final day of the world’s strongest team event. The race to be the best team in the world is coming to its crowing point. All is still wide open for any of these to take the title. Who is going to win? Will team Latvia keep their World Title or maybe Finland can attach them? Keep watching and we’ll find out.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E08 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 8, Esposende
programme.desc: Welcome back to Strongman Champions League for another stage of the 2022 world tour. We’re in Esposende - Portugal in this beautiful setting next to the beach in front of a packed crowd with some of the strongest men the world has to offer. With a real Porsche deadlift and many other crazy stuff. So, lets get this show started.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E09 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 9, Great Britain
programme.desc: Hello and welcome in Gloucester, UK. The world tour hasn’t been here for what feels like forever. And now for the first time in the Mekka of Strongman, the SCL World series will crown a great Champion with the SCL Title. It will be full with special wooden events, and a great winner! So ladies and gentleman, boys and girls, brace yourselves because I present to you strongman champions league UK.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E10 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 10, Poland Part 1
programme.desc: We are in Sopot, Poland the home of Legends Mariusz Pudzianowkski and Krzystof Radzikowski. Who will grab the title here in holiday resort Sopot, on the great Balrtic Sea with 6 events and 12 athlets in the mix!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E11 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 11, Poland Part 2
programme.desc: We are in Sopot, Poland, after 3 events the Polish Strongman Oskar Ziolkowski is Leading. Kelvin, Travis and Aivars are coming up and will try to beat him, but will Oskar take his first title ever?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E12 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 12, Bosnia
programme.desc: it’s been a long time since the world series held a championship here in Sarajevo. Let’s see what test of strength this destination holds for our athletes. And what fantastic athletes are here again in Stage 12 of the SCL World Series. The strongman champions league Bosnia is another iconic Strongman event with the return of Rongo Keen from Australia and Portugal winner 2022 George Sulaiman.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E13 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 13, Romania
programme.desc: Welcome to Sibiu in Romania. It’s an important day for some of these athletes, because four of them have a real chance of getting into our all-exclusive world finals. There’s only one more stage after this to get those all-important extra points. So, there’s going to be some fireworks, who will take the title here and who will qualify for the World Finals?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E14 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 14, Gibraltar
programme.desc: This is it the last show before the world final. These guys have really got to fight for the points now, this is going to be action packed, whilst these guys fight it out all day.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E15 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 15, Turkey Part 1
programme.desc: We are in Alanya, on Turkey’s south-coast for the final stop at the end of a mammoth season of Strongman Champions League. Here in the sunshine, we’ll finally crown our world champion and what a place Alanya is. You could not ask for a better setting. After months of hard-work, if not years for some of these lads, we find out who will take the world title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S08 : E16 SCL 2022 Season 8, Episode 16, Turkey Part 1
programme.desc: Welcome, to day two of the strongman champions league 2022 finals here in Alanya, Turkey. It’s all up for grabs now, everyone is fighting for the world title belt. This is an epic episode where we finally crown the World champion of 2022.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E01 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 1 - Finland
programme.desc: Welcome to the 2023 Strongman Champions League in Vaasa, Finland! This year’s event introduces a knockout format with 6 intense events over 90 minutes, ending in a unique deadlift face-off with boats.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E02 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 2 - Serbia
programme.desc: Stage 2 of the Strongman Champions League 2023 is set in Zrenjanin, Serbia. This exciting event features 5 challenging contests, including a superhuman Yoke race. As the SCL World Series Tour continues, athletes will battle it out to claim the yellow leader’s position for the season. Don’t miss this incredible stage of strength and endurance!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E03 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 3 - Finland Teams World
programme.desc: The World’s Strongest Team will be crowned in this edition of SCL, here in Kalajoki-Finland we’ve picked some of the best in the business, teamed them up, and they’ll be going all out against each other. It’s now no longer about being a lonely wolf, but more about the pack mentality. It is a competition over 7 events, including a Big 2-man Log lift and heavy deadlift. Let’s start the action.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E04 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 4 - Holland
programme.desc: Strongman Champions League in Holland at the Dru Factory in ULFT. A great location for a spectacular battle with 14 Athletes over 3 events! The first 3 events in this episode are Truckpull/ Superyoke and Farmerswalk, with 2 massive logs of 150 kg in their hands. So, join us for the show of strength, the place of power, it’s the circus of the extreme.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E05 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 5 - Holland 2023
programme.desc: Ladies and gentleman, boys and girls, strongman fans across the world, we are back for SCL Holland part two. Get ready because it’s about to get heavy. The Strongman Champions League in Holland, continues with the last 3 events, here at the Dru Factory in ULFT. The events in this episode are the Viking Press, Wheel Flip and the Atlas Stones, with 180 kg in the end.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E06 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 6 - Worlds Strongest Latino
programme.desc: For the first time ever, the World’s Strongest Latino competition has begun. This two-day event in Porto, Portugal, features 20 athletes from around the world competing in 8 events. After 4 grueling events, the top 12 will advance to the finals.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E07 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 7 - Finland World Record Breakers
programme.desc: Strongman Champions League World Record Breakers 2023 starts with a 25-ton snow plow! Crazy machines are pulled and pushed, with many kilograms moved. A few new world records are set in this competition.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E08 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 8 - Portugal
programme.desc: We have returned to the powerhouse of Portugal for an edge-of-your-seat galactic battle. If all the planets collided at once, it wouldn’t compare to the bang of this show. Get ready for the battle of the beasts; it’s the heaviest show in the universe, the Strongman Champions League.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S09 : E09 SCL 2023 Season 9, Stage 9 - England
programme.desc: SCL UK has landed in Gloucester it is workout war fitness for the ferocious, it’s going to be a a battle of the brutal, a rampage of the roofless. This is going to be a massacre of the muscles. You know it by now, but just in case you don’t, this is strongman champions league.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

Forfattaren trodde att han skrev om framtiden, men i sjalva verket var det det forflutna. I hans roman åker ett tåg till 2046 lite då och då. Alla som åkte dit hade samma intention: att återuppleva sina forlorade minnen. Det sades att 2046 andrade sig aldrig något. Ingen visste sakert om det var sant, eftersom ingen som åkte dit någonsin hade kommit tillbaka - utom en. Han var dar. Han valde att åka darifrån. Han ville forandras.

programme.title: I Heart Huckabees
programme.desc: Albert Markovski ar ledare for Open Spaces Coalition och han har upplevt en orovackande rad av sammantraffanden som han inte forstår inneborden av. Med hjalp av de två existentiella detektiverna Bernard och Vivian Jaffe undersoker Albert sitt liv, sina relationer och sin konflikt med Brad Stand, en foretagsledare som klattrar på karriarstegen på Huckabees, en popular varuhuskedja.

programme.title: The Fifth Estate
programme.desc: De borjade med att skapa en undergroundwebbplats och kom att bli varldens mest efterlysta personer. Men nar WikiLeaksgrundarnaJulian Assange och Daniel Domscheit-Berg kom over den storsta mangden sekretessbelagd underrattelseinformation som någonsin har lackt ut från det amerikanska forsvarsministeriet borjade en intern kamp. For vad ar priset for den fria varldens storsta hemligheter? Och vad kommer det att kosta att avsloja dem?

programme.title: What Maisie Knew
programme.desc: Maisie måste navigera i ett vuxen kaos med all sin oskuld, charm och villkorslosa karlek nar hon fastnar i mitten av foraldrarnas bittra vårdnadstvist. Den alltid observante Maisie kastas fram och tillbaka mellan sina foraldrar, Susanna, en åldrande rockstjarna, som jagar en sista ""hit"" och fadern Beale som ar en upptagen konsthandlare med många resdagar. Båda gifter sig med nya partners for att bli starkare i en vårdnadstvist samtidigt som Maisie knyter allt starkare band mellan sig o mammans nya pojkvan, bartendern Lincoln, inser hon att hon måste vara den vuxna i sin egen lilla familj.

programme.title: Elektra
programme.desc: Marvels femme fatale; Elektra (Garner) bevisar att utseende kan doda nar den sexigaste actionhjalten någonsin bryter sig ut från serietidningssidorna till filmduken. I sitt nya uppdrag tvingas hon fatta ett odesdigert beslut i kampen mellan gott och ont!

programme.title: Im Not There
programme.desc: Dylan gestaltas i denna film av vitt skilda skådespelare/skådesperskor i en serie av sammanvavda historier. "Im Not There" ar ett ovanligt och enastående portratt av Amerikas storste nu levande rockikon, Bob Dylan. Ovanligt eftersom hela sex skådespelare, unga som gamla, kvinnor som man och svarta som vita gestaltar Dylan. Enastående eftersom filmen ar den enda av många filmer om Dylan, som har fått legendens eget godtyckande och darmed den gyllene nyckeln till ett musikarkiv av narmast mytologisk karaktar. Resultatet ar en fenomenalt vacker hyllning till Bob Dylan och hans musik, och en fantastisk inblick i en musikalisk enstorings liv, som både fans och nyborjare kan gladjas over.

programme.desc: En komisk vriden historia om en dysfunktionell familj som samlas for att sorja sin patriarks bortgång. Daniels far har just avlidit och det enda han vill ar att genomfora begravningen som planerat, vilket inte ar det lattaste med en galen familj på halsen. Brorsan ar mest intresserad av att ragga tjejer, en annan slakting ar overtygad om att fadern ar vid liv i kistan och en mystisk pillerburk dyker standigt upp. Denna dråpliga komedi i brittisk tradition bjuder på många overraskningar.

programme.title: The Wind
programme.desc: Under det sena 1800-talet flyttar en kvinna med sin man till den amerikanska vastern for att starta ett nytt liv. Men nar hon lamnas ensam i det tomma huset gor den hårda omgivningen och isoleringen henne orolig, eller rent ut sagt paranoid. Eller ar det faktiskt något verkligt, något overnaturligt som besitter de karga vidderna?

programme.title: Lost Highway
programme.desc: Fred Madison och hans fru Renee hittar mystiska videoband på verandan, på banden syns deras hus. Forst filmat utifrån. På nasta, inifrån. Polisen ar inte intresserade av att hjalpa paret, men nar annu ett videoband dyker upp och visar Renees dod vacks i stallet misstankarna mot Fred. Och darifrån ska ingenting komma att bli mindre mardromslikt. Lost Highway ar en neonoirthriller av en David Lynch i hogform, med Bill Pullman (Independence Day) och Oscarsbelonade Patricia Arquette (Boyhood) i huvudrollerna.

Vad som borjar som bara en vanlig arbetsdag forvandlas snabbt till en kamp på liv och dod for en mjuk och tystlåten amerikansk co-pilot nar en grupp terrorister forsoker ta kontroll over hans flygning mot Paris. Nu måste han kampa – inte bara for sitt eget liv, utan for passagerarnas och besattningens – genom att forsoka skapa en unik kontakt med en av kaparna. Omid Memar medverkar också.

programme.title: Xplore Bulgaria
programme.desc: Like Rome, Plovdiv straddles seven hills; but as Europe’s oldest continuously inhabited city, it’s far more ancient. Along the way, she realizes why Plovdiv is called the ‘Eternal City’ of Bulgaria.

In Crimea, a mountain has been carved into a james bondian submarine base. In northern Ukraine, the Chernobyl nuclear site has been reduced to a radioactive wasteland.

programme.title: Destination Okinawa
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Blue Zones of Longevity - Season 1 - Destination Okinawa
programme.desc: Genetic, biological, cultural and dietary factors combine to make the Japanese island of Okinawa a zone of extreme longevity. Why is it that cancer is virtually non-existent here? Well see that the famous Japanese trio of "rice, fish and soy" is not the key to longevity, but a diet based on plants, lots of green leafy vegetables and endemic sweet potatoes. Self-restriction and strong social ties are other elements that our naturopathic chef and attending physician will discover on site, together with local inhabitants and scientists.

programme.title: USA: The end of oil - Part 2
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - USA: The end of oil - Part 2
programme.desc: "The end of oil" is the amazing story of a raw material which has revolutionized mans life in just a century. But today, oil reserves are depleting. In his crazy race for always more production, Man didnt manage to preserve this precious energy that took million years for the Earth to give out. To tell the adventure of oil, Yann Arthus-Bertrand and his team went to the United States, the country which depends the most on black gold. programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Carine (Nice)
programme.desc: After twenty years as a lawyer, Carine decided to give in to her desire to help others heal. Her inner journey led her to discover a passion for naturopathy as she rediscovered her love for nature and learned the healing qualities of the plants around her. Combined with a deep understanding of astrology and nutrition, she is now able to help others live better and find their own path.

programme.title: Virginie (Lyon)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Virginie (Lyon)
programme.desc: Virginie’s beautiful handwritten lettering decorates the walls and windows of many shops in and around Lyon, France, as she lives out her passion of finding beauty in every stroke. A former waitress, Virginie was struggling to find her calling when she suffered a life-altering horse accident that almost left her handicapped. At only 30, she was forced to put her whole life into perspective. She finally found herself through a love for graphic design and lettering, combined with a desire for freedom that came with working independently. To motivate other women, she has also launched “Ladyboss”, a network of inspiring women entrepreneurs.

programme.title: Laetitia (French Alps)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Laetitia (French Alps)
programme.desc: While pregnant with her daughter, Laetitia, a former journalist, experienced a strong desire to change lifestyles and move to the countryside. Remembering the teachings of her grandmother, she began to venture outdoors into the surrounding Alps and study the different plants at her fingertips. Today she holds a wealth of knowledge about the medicinal and aromatherapeutic value of plants that she applies to making natural products. With utmost respect for the environment, Laetitia gathers only what she needs in order to make herbal infusions.

programme.title: Louise (Oleron Island)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Louise (Oleron Island)
programme.desc: At only 20 years old, Louise is full of confidence and already achieved a personal dream of hers to share her passion for nutritious and locally-sourced ingredients on the island of Oleron, France. Repurposing a camping car, she set up a brunch and tea-time spot where the guests can hand-pick their ingredients in the adjacent organic fields. Louise transforms the ingredients into favourite creations of hers and even joins her father for boat trips when she needs to stock up on fresh fish for the menu!

programme.title: Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 1
programme.desc: In this instalment, Yann Arthus-Bertrand lifts the veil on the products people buy. Almost everything we buy has a direct impact on our environment. We head to Japan to talk about the impact of new technologies, then to the Republic of Congo in Bukavu for the coltan harvest. How does our total consumption affect the environment? What permanent brands are we imposing on our planet? How can we differentiate between useful and useless purchases?

Her adventure will lead her through the Libourne region, then onwards to the North of France, the Ardèche, and the Aisne, where bakers have transformed bread into a powerful catalyst for social cohesion. While some individuals may avoid bread, particularly due to gluten-related concerns, others have chosen to reposition it at the forefront of the dining experience by championing its nutritional benefits. This commitment is shared by several chefs whom Julie will meet at the conclusion of her expedition.
